  "critical": false,
  "description": "Farming Black Soldier Fly larvae (Hermetia illucens) for protein meal and biowaste conversion. BSF larvae convert 1 ton of organic waste into 150-200 kg of fresh larvae (40-45% protein dry weight) in 14-18 days, providing high-protein feed for chickens, fish, and pigs while reducing waste volume by 50-80%.",
  "early_win": true,
  "early_win_note": "Converts food waste and manure into high-protein animal feed within 2 weeks. The fastest protein production cycle in any livestock system.",
